# NAME: china-direct
# AUTHOR: Ai intelligent assistant
# UPDATED: 2026-05-31
# PURPOSE: Surge 5 iOS rule set for China mainland services that should use DIRECT.
#
# Usage in Surge profile:
#   [Rule]
#   RULE-SET,china-direct.list,DIRECT
#   GEOIP,CN,DIRECT
#   FINAL,PROXY
#
# Notes:
# - This is a rule-set file, so rules below do not include a policy name.
# - Keep GEOIP,CN in the main [Rule] section if you also want China IP ranges direct.

